ServerCyde,is,a,service,that,allows,users,to,build,web,application,features,without,server,configuration,Some,features,included,with,ServerCyde,service,are,data,storage,social,network,authentication,real,time,messaging,in,applications,and,email,functionality,The,ServerCyde,API,allows,developers,to,access,the,functionality,of,ServerCyde,for,integration,with,other,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,publishing,websites,pushing,out,emails,and,broadcasts,building,contact,forms,and,creating,email,templates